<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٣ ليست في الأصل و<span class="c1">"ط"</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٤ ليست في <span class="c1">"ب"</span> و<span class="c1">"س"</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٥ ليست في <span class="c1">"ط"</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>